            "type": "text",
            "text": "BGE M3, from BAAI, is a multilingual embedding model optimized for efficiency with FP16 precision, reducing memory usage while maintaining accuracy. Key aspects include support for over 100 languages and compatibility with batch inference, making it ideal for API services handling diverse requests. Deploy it as a containerized microservice to ensure scalability and isolation."
