          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrate BGE M3 by exposing RESTful endpoints for embedding generation. Use asynchronous processing for batch requests to optimize throughput, and implement robust error handling with retries for transient failures. Ensure API gateways manage rate limiting and authentication to maintain security and reliability."
          }
        ]
      },
