            "text": "Scaling and Monitoring for Production Reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Scale horizontally by deploying multiple BGE M3 instances behind a load balancer, adjusting based on traffic patterns. Monitor critical metrics such as request latency, error rates, and resource utilization using tools like Prometheus. Regularly update the model and dependencies to address performance regressions and security vulnerabilities."
